<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<em><strong>No spoilers here, please. <p>
NO SPOILERS HERE!</em></strong> 
</p>
<p>
A Warrior is a hack-and-slash character, who solves most of his problems by cutting them to pieces, but who will occasionally fall back on the help  of a magical device. A Warrior's prime stats are Strength and Constitution,  and a good Dexterity can really help at times. A Warrior will be good  at Fighting and Throwing/Bows, but bad at most other skills. 
</p>
<p>
A Warrior learns no magic. 
</p>
<p>
Starting stat modifiers, starting Skills, innate abilities and starting equipment: Please see the in-game help. 
</p>
